To between one and ten x: i32, giving i1.
Give x is greater than or equal to 1 and x is less than or equal to 10.

To outside one and ten x: i32, giving i1.
Give x is less than 1 or x is greater than 10.

To main, giving i32.
Give 7 when between one and ten 7 and not outside one and ten 7; otherwise 1.
